50:57.821 --> 51:02.159 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And just the say he said that,
too, is so
indicative of Mr. Rogers.

51:02.192 --> 51:04.661 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He didn't say, oh, what was
bothering you?

51:04.694 --> 51:06.263 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
He said, "Would you like to tell
me?"

51:06.296 --> 51:07.731 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
And I did.

51:07.764 --> 51:11.268 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And it helped so much just to
have someone
to talk to.

51:11.301 --> 51:14.671 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It wasn't just a persona that he
put on for
this program.

51:14.704 --> 51:20.744 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
