like this.

51:27.317 --> 51:31.755 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that quote that he gave
repeatedly in
interviews about his mother
telling him, if

51:31.788 --> 51:36.526 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
