are hurting.

51:40.297 --> 51:45.368 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I saw that meme, like a
photograph of
him with that text shared again
and again

51:45.402 --> 51:47.137 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
by different people online.

51:47.170 --> 51:51.475 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that just got me thinking of
this memory
of how Mr. Rogers was kind in
real life.

51:51.508 --> 51:55.779 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I don't think anybody could ever
fill Mr.
Rogers' shoes.

51:55.812 --> 51:57.180 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
We can try.

51:57.214 --> 51:59.316 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
But he was one of a kind.

51:59.349 --> 52:02.018 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And once in a lifetime means
